text.section:
The Hippodrome Performing Arts Fund consists of:
funds appropriated for deposit to the Hippodrome Performing Arts Fund;
proceeds from the sale of bonds concerning the Hippodrome Performing Arts facility;
revenues collected or received from any source under this subtitle concerning the Hippodrome Performing Arts facility; and
any additional money made available from any public or private source for the purposes established for the Hippodrome Performing Arts Fund.
